There is no such group as "De Nye Gitarkameratene" --  so please stop using that term. Their legal name is "Lind, Nilsen, Fuentes, Holm". Gitarkameratene is a name that belongs to a Norwegian supergroup made up of Lillebjørn Nilsen, Halvdan Sivertsen, Jan Eggum and Øystein Sunde.
